Extra.description:
Extra options. JSON array may contain parameters (the first 3 are required):

<b>success_url</b> - success url;
<b>decline_url</b> - decline url;
<b>cancel_url</b> – return url (return 'button');
<b>account_id</b> – to return directly to the client's office;

Example: 
{"success_url": "http://server1.com/", "decline_url": "http://server2.com/", "cancel_url": "http://server3.com/", “account_id”: “1122aass112”}

In the case of the automatic redirect of the customer: 

<b>success_url</b> - url for redirect after a successful transaction;
<b>decline_url</b> - url for redirect after a decline transaction;
